Example....NIST:

Audit Prep:
Relevant Framework resources i.e. 800-171 Excel spreadsheet.
Identify points of contact.
Review the assessment points and understand what they mean.

Audit Logistics:
Who do you need to talk to.
If assessment criteria align with different areas i.e. HR and Server team then consolidate the meeting.
How Long.
Request SOP documentation in advance and example.

Audit (on-site):
Concise
Respect Time

Post Audit Reconciliation:

Analysis:
Make an assessment on each control

Reporting:

Executive Summary
Purpose
Scope
Who was interviewed
What was audited i.e. 900-171
Link your assessment material i.e Spreedsheet
Results
Conclusion
